# Fixture template for the gitleaks-rejects-fake-key test (Plan 09 / Task: test_gitleaks).
#
# DO NOT rename this file to leaked_key.txt and commit it.
# tests/fixtures/leaked_key.txt is gitignored.
#
# The pytest case copies this file's content into a tmp file and asserts that
# `gitleaks detect --no-git --source=<tmpfile> --config=.gitleaks.toml`
# exits non-zero (i.e. the leak IS detected).
#
# The string below is the canonical OpenAI test/sentinel pattern. It is NOT a real key
# and matches the same regex shape gitleaks scans for; the allowlist above intentionally
# does not cover this exact form.
sk-proj-AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA
